\sum^\infty_{n=1}(-1)^nnx^n
|\frac{a_{n+1}}{a_n}| = |\frac{(-1)^{n+1}(n+1)x^n}{(-1)^n(n)x^n}| = |\frac{-1(n+1)}{n}| = |\frac{-n-1}{n}|= |-1 -\frac{1}{n}|
|-1|
